{"tid":2170037,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"世衛更新指引，建議12歲或以上兒童及青少年戴口罩","createTime":"2020-08-23T03:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T14:15:41.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"06f5d30f15b60e46eff6fd9a0272fd3dac5f1391","tid":2170037,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織針對新型肺炎疫情，更新指引，建議12歲或以上的兒童及青少年，需要佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n新指引指這個年齡層的人，在相同情況下應該與成年人一樣佩戴口罩，特別是當他們未能保證能夠與其他人，至少保持1米距離，以及身處地區出現廣泛傳播的疫情。<br />\n<br />\n新指引又說較年輕的兒童，可以根據情況，決定是否戴口罩，<strong>但強調不應要求5歲及以下兒童戴口罩。世衛又說</strong>，各地民眾應時常諮詢所屬地區當局有關戴口罩的指引。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545324-20200822.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545324-20200822.htm&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=898dad9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545324-20200822.htm&h=8f30d7ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545324-20200822.htm</a>"},{"pid":"15cd63f23aeab9d745d7a5004b4de5a6f7e81ce9","tid":2170037,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-nZ6shpjsCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-nZ6shpjsCs&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=85604c4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-nZ6shpjsCs</a><br />\n<br />\n＃831<br />\n還有一星期凝聚大家<br />\n如果感動到你   或者你覺得感動到人<br />\n幫手周圍post周圍forward<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\n你講一句，我將佢變成音樂，但今次有d唔同<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2169984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2169984</a>"},{"pid":"f65044caa8ae1f65a1a90aff4a2867d1f911d4f4","tid":2170037,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"